Be careful of grapefruit, orange and apple juice.
These drinks, which are consumed in summer due to their refreshing quality and vitamin richness, especially in summer, can cause serious health damage if they are taken at the same time with certain vital medicines, as they can have an extreme effect on the absorption of these by the body.
